ill write another mail later, on the meaning of Parashu Rama's story. As I =
said before, Parashu Rama is Venus. Venus shows the spirit of happiness wit=
hin us. So Parashu Rama's life teaches us various things about happiness in=
 general. I will throw light on it later.

